Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小葵的鑰匙喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鑰匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要動手咯  作戰開始
