Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Texture ON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也變身成功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小島被…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真敢下手呢
